//·········································第一段
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"> 
<title>css</title> 
<style>
h1,h2,p
{
	color:green;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<h1>Hello World!</h1>
<h2>Smaller heading!</h2>
<p>This is a paragraph.</p>
</body>
</html>
//·············································第二段
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"> 
<title>css</title> 
<style>
p
{
	color:blue;
	text-align:center;
}
.marked
{
	background-color:red;
}
.marked p
{
	color:white;
}
p.marked{
    text-decoration:underline;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<p>这个段落是蓝色文本，居中对齐。</p>
<div class="marked">
<p>这个段落不是蓝色文本。</p>
</div>
<p>所有 class="marked"元素内的 p 元素指定一个样式，但有不同的文本颜色。</p>
	
<p class="marked">带下划线的 p 段落。</p>
</body>
</html>
